Problem definition Istio and the underlying Kubernetes platform create a sealed ecosystem, where control plane and data plane components are tightly integrated. For example, control plane components running on each node create a mutually trusted relationship. When new pods are scheduled to run on a node, the node is a trusted entity and its critical resources, like iptables, are modified.

